  "texts": [
    "The disagreements were resolved through discussions.",
    "464 queries out of 1500 were identified as HIGH sensitivity queries from a data leakage perspective.",
    "The manually rephrased versions of these 464 queries were added back to the dataset with T 1 label as \"LOW\" (and T 2 /T 3 labels as NA), making the final effective dataset size to be of 1964 queries.",
    "Figure 2 shows the distribution of the 6 data leakage types and Table 6 (in Appendix) shows a few examples of these annotations.",
    "We explored encoder-only models only for Tasks T 1 and T 3 which are binary classification and multi-label multi-class classification tasks, respectively."
  ],
